content.text:
<button class="shopping-list-item-quantity-button -decrement" type="button"
        ng-click="decrement();"
        ng-disabled="tempQuantity <= min"
        title="Decrease Quantity" tabindex="-1"
        data-qa="shopping-list-item-quantity-decrement"></button>

<input shopping-list-item-quantity-input="" class="shopping-list-item-quantity-input" type="text"
       name="quantityInput" ng-model="tempQuantity" pattern="\d*"
       ng-blur="callModelChange()"
       ng-keyup="$event.keyCode == 13 && callModelChange()"
       ng-change="callInputChange()"
       title="Edit Quantity"
       data-qa="shopping-list-item-quantity-input"/>

<button class="shopping-list-item-quantity-button -increment" type="button"
        ng-click="increment();"
        ng-disabled="tempQuantity >= max" tabindex="-1"
        title="Increase Quantity" data-qa="shopping-list-item-quantity-increment"></button>
